{"tid":1480751,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為宣布開發6G技術，會與加拿大合作研究","createTime":"2019-08-17T12:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T16:15:34.000Z","uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f5b62c68ca1ed8cf9fe6cd3954c648ffa9944052","tid":1480751,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"受到中美貿易戰的影響，華為在科技界上處處受到封鎖，除了手機軟硬件上被限制外，更限制了各地的網絡商使用華為的 <strong>5G</strong> 技術，而現在就有最新的消息，就是華為 Huawei 宣佈，將會在加拿大展開 <strong>6G</strong> 研究。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/dynimagecache/0/79/3000/1695/1024/578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aefimagesnew/aef_image/2019-05-21t131430z_1586202012_rc1484a93f90_rtrmadp_3_huawei-usa-5g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fdynimagecache%2F0%2F79%2F3000%2F1695%2F1024%2F578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faefimagesnew%2Faef_image%2F2019-05-21t131430z_1586202012_rc1484a93f90_rtrmadp_3_huawei-usa-5g.jpg&h=f3c5fd36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前 Samsung 、Nokia 及美國公司都先後表示，要開發下一世代的網絡技術 <strong>6G</strong>，現在華為為了追上世界發展，宣佈將會在加拿大渥太華實驗室展開 <strong>6G</strong> 研究。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/6G.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F6G.jpeg&h=55d46572&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前因為 <strong>6G</strong> 處於開發階段，因此目前對 <strong>6G</strong> 的要求、技術等，都沒有統一的標準數據，而美國聯邦通信委員會 FCC 則決定，將會開放指定頻段，讓各大廠商可以進行 <strong>6G</strong> 的測試及開發工作。<br />\n <img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/gsmarena_001-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2Fgsmarena_001-2.jpg&h=109ae650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而 <strong>5G</strong> 技術上，華為的最大對手，就是來自芬蘭的 Nokia ，在 <strong>5G</strong> 技術上，兩大公司所簽的合作公司數量極之相近，因此預計在 <strong>6G</strong> 的開發上，Nokia 亦會是華為的主要對手。"},{"pid":"1f68a34523f7991937fbaef7a620723e7d3e137d","tid":1480751,"uid":33886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"read"},{"pid":"a34b76f26564f64421ab998f865d1edfea584ee3","tid":1480751,"uid":269537,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"其實都唔知會唔會上6G<br />\n4G基本上解決手機上需求<br />\n5G基本上處理入屋同商用物聯<br />\n6G就睇下用係邊啦"},{"pid":"3ea1b97b752a056a0052c8068f8f09d945e134b0","tid":1480751,"uid":159448,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a34b76f26564f64421ab998f865d1edfea584ee3","tid":1480751,"uid":269537,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"其實都唔知會唔會上6G<br />\n4G基本上解決手機上需求<br />\n5G基本上處理入屋同商用物聯<br />\n6G就睇下用係邊啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:30:44.000Z","msg":"太空"},{"pid":"eadc42feabaddbf1fa2363b17dab82f998eee100","tid":1480751,"uid":299984,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:31:43.000Z","msg":"叫中共放撚左啲加拿大籍被捕人士先啦屌"},{"pid":"3a92484ec6445c1f8f980df5dfa5b74b027d68d9","tid":1480751,"uid":217275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:33:44.000Z","msg":"到時洗撚核武<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲幅射勁撚到"},{"pid":"ed97f2bbc5750975148030df3dd56c62d5fa6327","tid":1480751,"uid":70336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:40:45.000Z","msg":"外國整好？咁快有得抄？"},{"pid":"ac9580ec4f21acb757690442e329f6c539c92bba","tid":1480751,"uid":88029,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ed04b93b3cd914985396296312f269874b0be53","tid":1480751,"uid":56731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ed97f2bbc5750975148030df3dd56c62d5fa6327","tid":1480751,"uid":70336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:40:45.000Z","msg":"外國整好？咁快有得抄？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"依家係咪都話自己研究緊，到時抄完人偷完技術咪光明正大話係自己野"},{"pid":"902fda